Marisol (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marisol_(actress) 0 Josefa Flores González (born 4 February 1948), known professionally as Marisol or Pepa Flores, is a retired Spanish singer and actress, who was popular during the 1960s in Spain, a former child and teen star.
